    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344070/extras/d23d7b13219169f2124009eacb264e3f.poster.avif?t=1770384100\" width=320 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344070/extras/d23d7b13219169f2124009eacb264e3f.webm?t=1770384100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344070/extras/d23d7b13219169f2124009eacb264e3f.mp4?t=1770384100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >序言</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许是突然出现、也许早有预兆。一种奇特的疾病根纹症开始在世界上流行，同时世界各地自然灾害频发，人类陷入恐慌与不安中。因感染根纹症而失忆的主角多塞珥需要尽快找到治疗疾病的方法。侵入大脑的病症时刻威胁着自己的生命，在“友人们”的协助下，多塞珥前往家族的旧宅，那里的地下研究所中也许存在着治疗的药物。而与解药一起被找寻的，还有那些丢失的记忆与埋藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >脑海中回响的呼唤，到底来自何处？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344070/extras/0fe124d0316602c3968f17687fd235a2.webp?t=1770384100\" width=657 height=57 /></span>《梦兆温室》是一款含有恐怖要素的视觉小说+RPG场景探索类游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将与主角多塞珥·亨特一起见证各种各样的梦境与回忆，一边寻找治疗身体的方法，一边重新认识身边的友人，在旅途中了解家族的历史与末日的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344070/extras/055adba2887d915d79f7901e9b3ec4cf.webp?t=1770384100\" width=657 height=57 /></span>♦ 丰富的剧情内容和大量CG插画，全篇共7个章节，计划将有6个结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♦ 在视觉小说的叙事基础上，融入了RPG探索和少量QTE、解谜环节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♦ 含有原创音乐与轻量的音游要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♦ 特设的收集页面，除主线剧情之外，通过收集“回忆碎片”可以了解更多关于角色们的小故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344070/extras/d4e5425c1f4aa86cfbad3c69267c59fa.webp?t=1770384100\" width=657 height=57 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344070/extras/52226f09f86c10e8af96752f9e97cea1.avif?t=1770384100\" width=656 height=370 /></span><strong>多塞珥·亨特</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Docile·Hunter</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  故事的主角。一位因感染根纹症而失去了部分记忆的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  总是会做噩梦。对“海”有种异样的执着。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  为了寻找失去的记忆与治疗疾病的方法，与友人们踏上了</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344070/extras/de9e3aba399133cfb17e6f53f26b722d.avif?t=1770384100\" width=656 height=370 /></span><strong>乔纳森·乔布斯  ＆  厄拉卡多·琼斯</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jonathan·Jobs ＆ Erracado·Jones</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  居住在「花园」中的二人，身份神秘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  主角的旧识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  照顾着主角并帮其寻找治疗根纹症的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344070/extras/99ae305bf9341267c595489f6dba99cd.avif?t=1770384100\" width=656 height=370 /></span><strong>利多卡因·里德  ＆  伊德·里德</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lidocaine·Reed ＆ Ether·Reed</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  某家私立医院的医生兼管理者，其中一人处于失踪状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  主角的旧识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  了解许多关于根纹症的信息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344070/extras/e6c869abd4372c4ffca9e4edd0af79b4.avif?t=1770384100\" width=656 height=370 /></span><strong>格莱克希·斯卡拉德纳  ＆  萍琪·弗雷泽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Galaxy·Scaradner ＆ Pinkie·Fraser</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  不为人知的地下研究所的工作者们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  与主角来自同一个家族。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·  为了解救同事向主角寻求帮助，声称拥有治愈根纹症的解药可作为交换。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※游戏为业余制作，因制作人员（仅2人）年初工作调动问题影响，正式发布日期有延迟。请以社团公告为准。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
